tr 'A-Za-z' 'N-ZA-Mn-za-m' < data.txt 

tr		: Translates or replaces characters.
'A-Za-z'	: Matches all uppercase and lowercase letters.
'N-ZA-Mn-za-m'	: Maps letters to their equivalents 13 positions ahead (ROT13).
< input.txt	: Specifies the input file.


